snippet.title: Quiet Farm - Official Exclusive Gameplay Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2022
snippet.description:
Quiet Farm's new gameplay trailer shows how it's not exactly the quiet world you'd imagine it to be as a mysterious UFO crashes into the world. Playing as a cow, you must traverse the farm to protect your home and land from the alien invasion.

#IGN #Gaming #IGNSummerOfGaming
